title: Who Killed Julie Greer?
description: Amos Burke is an L.A. cop who's inherited millions and usually arrives at crime scenes in a chauffeur-driven Rolls-Royce. Investigating the death of actress Julie Greer, he finds lots of suspects - but the killer's identity surprises him.

title: The Fifth Caller
description: A murder mystery set in an English coastal town.

title: Price of Tomatoes
description: A truck driver on a very tight schedule stops to give a lift to a pregnant hitch-hiker; and then his life gets very complicated.

title: The Boston Terrier
description: An upper-crust Boston sleuth uses the very latest in scientific gadgetry when investigating a big-time gangster.

title: The Great Anatole
description: Anatole, the great magician, is a man of mystery - but just how mysterious really is he? Might he be a missing atom scientist?

title: The Court Martial of Captain Wycliff
Crazy Sunday
description: Tyro screenwriter Joel Coles makes a fool of himself at a Hollywood party, and finds out a few hard truths about life in the movie business.

title: The Big Day
description: Fred is the longest-serving employee of a big department store, and new management has decided it's time for him to go.

title: Thunder in a Forgotten Town
description: After ten years in a Red Chinese POW camp, John Reardon returns home.

title: The Third Side of a Coin
description: As blackmailers go, Rosalind is a most unusual one.

title: The Last of the Big Spenders
The Old Man and the City
Last of the Private Eyes
description: Kelly, a former cinema usher, wants to be a private eye; and he finds that life is just like the movies.
